item.title: CVE-2020-5627|2024-08-04T08:39:25.092Z -- yodobashi%20camera%20co.%2Cltd. -- yodobashi%20app%20for%20android
item.description: Yodobashi App for Android versions 1.8.7 and earlier allows remote attackers to lead a user to access an arbitrary website via the vulnerable App. As a result, the user may become a victim of a phishing attack.
